似的地方，但是《非暴力沟通》写得更加深刻。 为什么我们跟别人说话的时候容易出现暴力的状况？ 它从很深入的角度剖析了暴力的产生来源，并且给出了一个…\",\"image\":{\"image_url\":\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-89940490e09b14c8cfa336dec12c83af_720w.jpg\",\"ratio\":1,\"is_video\":false},\"bg_type\":\"dark\"},\"source\":{\"content_type\":\"ANSWER\",\"content_id\":\"1391997629\"},\"za_data\":{\"attach_info\":\"\"}}","https://www.zhihu.com/answer/1396207687":"{\"card_type\":\"card_1\",\"display\":{\"title\":\"有哪些电影是你觉得有机会时一定要在影院荧幕上看的？\",\"card_open_url\":\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/412653121/answer/1396207687\",\"desc\":\"7 赞同 · 6 评论 \\u003ca class=\\\"tag type_a\\\"\\u003e回答\\u003c/a\\u003e\",\"content\":\"\\u003ca class=\\\"text normal/bold\\\" data-color=\\\"#444444\\\" data-night-color=\\\"#D3D3D3\\\"\\u003e夏夜:\\u003c/a\\u003e 很多时候，我喜欢一个人在家看电影。 但是感觉总是缺了点什么？ 是氛围？是体验？还是一种在家体会不到的兴奋感？ 朋友之间的聚会，看电影是必不可少的一环节。我和朋友聚会时一般是先聚个餐，然后要么是选择去看电影，要么就去K歌。 现在回想起来，那时我们几个人一起去看电影是真的快乐。不管是那种处于黑暗中一群人环顾四周的空间氛围感，还是带着3D眼镜时那种将你的视力聚焦于荧幕上的专注力。这些东西在家是体验不到的。 况…\",\"image\":{\"image_url\":\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-511e969b6d69ede58a6ce2d0aca91738_720w.jpg\",\"ratio\":1,\"is_video\":false},\"bg_type\":\"dark\"},\"source\":{\"content_type\":\"ANSWER\",\"content_id\":\"1396207687\"},\"za_data\":{\"attach_info\":\"\"}}"},"question":{"created":1452747813,"id":39474276,"question_type":"normal","relationship":{},"title":"有哪些让你浑身颤抖、无法自拔，庆幸读到的好书？","type":"question","updated_time":1578563249,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276"},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_recognized":false,"is_thanked":false,"upvoted_followees":[],"voting":0},"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_text":"","relevant_type":""},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"description":"","note":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"status":""},"url":""},"type"