3e\u003cp data-pid=\"SspYJpDJ\"\u003e印象深刻的是这些作品\u003cbr/\u003e建议先看完书，再看电视剧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"hKt8aL5C\"\u003e(信)---一个杀人犯亲属的救赎之路\u003cbr/\u003e(秘密)----母女灵魂互换的奇幻故事，结局我哭了，非鸡汤，悲剧或喜剧取决于看书人自己\u003cbr/\u003e--已出电视剧，人物造型情节我给 100分\u003cbr/\u003e(幻夜)......在沙漠中遇到海市蜃楼，沉迷还是解脱，谁知道呢？\u003cbr/\u003e---已出电视剧，同样给100分\u003c/p\u003e","created_time":1489421881,"editable_content":"","excerpt":"看到这个问题之前的一分钟， 我正准备关掉手机盖被子来睡觉。但是看到了这个问题，我必须要来答一下 我最喜欢的书是东野圭吾的---恶意 [图片] 东叔的书迷很多， 大家可能更多的喜欢的是，白夜行(已出电视剧，白夜行人物多剧情多页数多，我啃了几次都没有啃完，感觉不适合刚接触长篇的读者)但是，它还是不及---恶意--- 给我带来的震撼感强烈，它能深深的让我入戏书中，不能自拔，热切的想知道最后的真相是什么，毫不拖沓的剧…","extras":"","id":151451465,"is_collapsed":false,"is_copyable":true,"is_labeled":false,"is_normal":true,"is_sticky":false,"question":{"created":1452747813,"id":39474276,"question_type":"normal","relationship":{},"title":"有哪些让你浑身颤抖、无法自拔，庆幸读到的好书？","type":"question","updated_time":1578563249,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276"},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_recognized":false,"is_thanked":false,"upvoted_followees":[],"voting":0},"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_text":"","relevant_type":""},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"description":"","note":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"status":""},"url":""},"type":"answer","updated_time":1558156414,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/151451465","voteup_count":331}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276/answers?data%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cvip_info%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics=\u0026data%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url=\u0026data%5B%2A%5D.settings.table_of_content.enabled=\u0026include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_