{"data":[{"admin_closed_comment":false,"annotation_action":null,"answer_type":"normal","author":{"avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-52a23e308bb8ffadaaab271dc531163e_l.jpg?source=1940ef5c","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-52a23e308bb8ffadaaab271dc531163e.jpg?source=1940ef5c","badge":[],"badge_v2":{"detail_badges":[],"icon":"","merged_badges":[],"night_icon":"","title":""},"gender":0,"headline":"在灵动和厚重之间找到平衡点","id":"ee7518b5e31f6fc35dc1fdb7d135814b","is_advertiser":false,"is_followed":false,"is_org":false,"is_privacy":false,"name":"Ekabhakti","type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ee7518b5e31f6fc35dc1fdb7d135814b","url_token":"zhou-jiu-10","user_type":"people"},"can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"collapse_reason":"","collapsed_by":"nobody","comment_count":66,"comment_permission":"all","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"YGuUjALT\"\u003e庆幸自己看到了很多好书\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"fQltj2Li\"\u003e  1. 杰克·伦敦的《热爱生命》，是一篇短篇小说。看完心情是相当沉重，觉得相比死去，活着真是困难千倍万倍的事情，所以生活艰难的时候，想起这本书就会振奋起来。《马丁·伊登》，杰克·伦敦的中篇小说，看完之后作者彻底成为了我心中最优秀的作家。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"L75-t0gE\"\u003e  2·王小波《沉默大多数》，《我的精神世界》看到了许许多多生活和自己的影子，觉得自己就是那个“傻大姐”ꉂ೭(˵¯̴͒ꇴ¯̴͒˵)౨”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"HK4QRRU4\"\u003e  3.狄更斯的《大卫·科波菲尔》，最喜欢的小说。爱格尼斯是我心中的女神，(๑′ᴗ‵๑)Ｉ Lᵒᵛᵉᵧₒᵤ   后来看B站狄更斯纪录片，介绍《大卫》是狄更斯最“宠爱的孩子”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"hFohcXfN\"\u003e  4.罗曼罗兰的《约翰·克里斯多夫》，从出生到去世，大部头，给我一种宽广的看待人生的视角\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"qlTPgNHn\"\u003e  5.拜伦的《唐璜》，虽是十四行诗，但是一点都不难读，语言直击骨髓。查良zheng翻译的（我忘了这个字怎么写了）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Kh28purO\"\u003e  6.三毛《亲爱的三毛》。这本书买过三次，一次送给我妹，她拆开快递的那一刻就给我电话，“能不能不要给我买这么幼稚的书”(⊙o⊙)…(⊙o⊙)…（原谅一下，我妹高中没毕业，不喜欢读书） 看完给我电话，“写的真有味道”……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"oDIUJXhU\"\u003e   喜欢民国时候的文人，《陈寅恪与傅斯年》让我觉得陈寅恪是最有风骨的文人，《梁思成自传》让我觉得林徽因是一个可爱的女子，周作人《雨中的书》雅致自然极了，梁实秋《雅舍小品》轻松愉悦，《傅雷家书》让我觉得家庭教育的重要性……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"UpiuqlUn\"\u003e   还有很多喜欢的，现在最想看的是普鲁斯特的《追忆似水年华》和一个朋友说的《知否 知否 应是绿肥红瘦》，然而木有时间\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Ul5FuReO\"\u003e   这个季节的深圳，写这点字手竟然冻僵了   \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"mPWbFNy0\"\u003e   来108遍拜日暖和暖和，哈哈哈……\u003c/p\u003e","created_time":1486647173,"editable_content":"","excerpt":"庆幸自己看到了很多好书 1. 杰克·伦敦的《热爱生命》，是一篇短篇小说。看完心情是相当沉重，觉得相比死去，活着真是困难千倍万倍的事情，所以生活艰难的时候，想起这本书就会振奋起来。《马丁·伊登》，杰克·伦敦的中篇小说，看完之后作者彻底成为了我心中最优秀的作家。 2·王小波《沉默大多数》，《我的精神世界》看到了许许多多生活和自己的影子，觉得自己就是那个“傻大姐”ꉂ೭(˵¯̴͒ꇴ¯̴͒…","extras":"","id":145446954,"is_collapsed":false,"is_copyable":true,"is_labeled":false,"is_normal":true,"is_sticky":false,"question":{"created":1452747813,"id":39474276,"question_type":"normal","relationship":{},"title":"有哪些让你浑身颤抖、无法自拔，庆幸读到的好书？","type":"question","updated_time":1578563249,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276"},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_recognized":false,"is_thanked":false,"upvoted_followees":[],"voting":0},"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_text":"","relevant_type":""},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"description":"","note":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"status":""},"url":""},"type":"answer","updated_time":1486647173,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/145446954","voteup_count":378}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276/answers?data%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cvip_info%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics=\u0026data%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url=\u0026data%5B%2A%5D.settings.table_of_content.enabled=\u0026include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cattachment%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2