{"data":[{"admin_closed_comment":false,"annotation_action":null,"answer_type":"normal","author":{"avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e8ee682bccb07ab47d41dc9f6c1c5ed5_l.jpg?source=1940ef5c","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e8ee682bccb07ab47d41dc9f6c1c5ed5.jpg?source=1940ef5c","badge":[],"badge_v2":{"detail_badges":[],"icon":"","merged_badges":[],"night_icon":"","title":""},"gender":0,"headline":"知名电影、电视剧观众","id":"e99f81d55bae759c84ecc8a04dcad33b","is_advertiser":false,"is_followed":false,"is_org":false,"is_privacy":false,"name":"公子词","type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e99f81d55bae759c84ecc8a04dcad33b","url_token":"chen-shu-ci","user_type":"people"},"can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"collapse_reason":"","collapsed_by":"nobody","comment_count":304,"comment_permission":"all","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"JZ0SNB75\"\u003e初中的时候误读了《洛丽塔》，在舅舅家一大柜子书堆里挑出来这么一本听名字就觉得很美的书。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"XnmZEacD\"\u003e翻开第一页就被惊艳到了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"jRuzi8mH\"\u003e永远记得读到那句开篇的震撼，无论过去多少年，无论再读几百遍，感受仍然一如当初。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"OCrYQoMi\"\u003e纳博科夫写道：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"KF42MCBk\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e“洛丽塔，我的生命之光，我的欲念之火。我的罪恶，我的灵魂。\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e洛—丽—塔：舌间向上，分三步，从上颚往下轻轻落在牙齿上。洛—丽—塔。”\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"BMc1oCXC\"\u003e当然英文版读起来更美：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Hd_AG2TP\"\u003e“Lolita, light of my life, fire of my loins. My sin, my soul. Lo-lee-ta: the tip of the tongue taking a trip of three steps down the palate to tap, at three, on the teeth. Lo. Lee. Ta.”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"-RMBJj2X\"\u003e我无法具体形容当时还是初中生的我读到这样一段话的感受。震撼、颤抖，不仅仅是因为那个故事，更多的是一个孩子对于文字力量的惊叹和拜服。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"YWAgYkpB\"\u003e这本书描写了一个恋童癖猥琐大叔和一个bitch萝莉的变态故事，读起来却没有一丝不适和反感。文字虚化了某种道德是非的界限，直接从感性层面提炼出灵魂深处的纯粹和美好，并且赤果果的展现在你面前。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"ysfDlO1n\"\u003e就那么短短两句话，直击心脏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"AwF2sXnB\"\u003e我是从那一天起发誓的，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"W_1ULWng\"\u003e将来一定要当一个作家。\u003c/p\u003e","created_time":1487473810,"editable_content":"","excerpt":"初中的时候误读了《洛丽塔》，在舅舅家一大柜子书堆里挑出来这么一本听名字就觉得很美的书。 翻开第一页就被惊艳到了。 永远记得读到那句开篇的震撼，无论过去多少年，无论再读几百遍，感受仍然一如当初。 纳博科夫写道： “洛丽塔，我的生命之光，我的欲念之火。我的罪恶，我的灵魂。 洛—丽—塔：舌间向上，分三步，从上颚往下轻轻落在牙齿上。洛—丽—塔。” 当然英文版读起来更美： “Lolita, light of my life, fire of my …","extras":"","id":147246304,"is_collapsed":false,"is_copyable":false,"is_labeled":false,"is_normal":true,"is_sticky":false,"question":{"created":1452747813,"id":39474276,"question_type":"normal","relationship":{},"title":"有哪些让你浑身颤抖、无法自拔，庆幸读到的好书？","type":"question","updated_time":1578563249,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276"},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_recognized":false,"is_thanked":false,"upvoted_followees":[],"voting":0},"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_text":"","relevant_type":""},"reshipment_settings":"disallowed","reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"description":"","note":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"status":""},"url":""},"type":"answer","updated_time":1506003512,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/147246304","voteup_count":3539}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/39474276/answers?data%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cvip_info%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics=\u0026data%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url=\u0026data%5B%2A%5D.settings.table_of_content.enabled=\u0026include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cattachment%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_p