{"data":[{"admin_closed_comment":false,"annotation_action":null,"answer_type":"normal","author":{"avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d8d7ea90ba9bfc93a402264f866dd642_l.jpg?source=1940ef5c","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d8d7ea90ba9bfc93a402264f866dd642.jpg?source=1940ef5c","badge":[],"badge_v2":{"detail_badges":[],"icon":"","merged_badges":[],"night_icon":"","title":""},"gender":1,"headline":"","id":"89d88a758d5da2df4457679ccf577a2b","is_advertiser":false,"is_followed":false,"is_org":false,"is_privacy":false,"name":"邵明","type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/89d88a758d5da2df4457679ccf577a2b","url_token":"hshaom","user_type":"people"},"can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"collapse_reason":"","collapsed_by":"nobody","comment_count":11,"comment_permission":"censor","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"YPHytZSa\"\u003e因为一句“永远年轻，永远热泪盈眶”，我知道了杰克·凯鲁亚克，因为知道了杰克·凯鲁亚克，我读到了他的代表作《在路上》，被深深震撼，以至于之后逢人便会极力推荐，并且强烈建议越早读到越好，因为这是一本属于年轻人的书。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"CM_LPLs7\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e凯鲁亚克的《在路上》\u003c/b\u003e，被誉为美国上世纪50、60年代垮掉派代表作。记得刚读完这本书时，我在微博上发感慨说：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote data-pid=\"n8XXw9jr\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e有一天我不再向别人提起这本书了，说明我的内心已腐朽不堪，动弹不得了。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a9e181f73622893b2311a85318e3dbd_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"854\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2a9e181f73622893b2311a85318e3dbd_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;750\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;854\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"854\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\"